data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Texarkana, AR! This exquisite 4-bedroom, 2-full bath traditional brick residence, nestled in the sought-after Trinity Heights Subdivision, is a perfect blend of style and functionality. Upon entering through the front door, you are greeted by the inviting formal living space seamlessly connected to the elegant formal dining area. A striking double-sided fireplace serves as a stylish focal point, artfully separating these two distinct living areas. Moving beyond the fireplace, you'll discover the cozy family room, thoughtfully designed to flow effortlessly into the well-appointed kitchen, breakfast nook and breakfast bar, providing a variety of dining options for your family and guests.  With a total of 2,039 sqft, this residence offers ample space for comfortable living. Beautiful neutral colors throughout the home enhance the feeling of warmth and sophistication.  The heart of the home lies within this beautiful kitchen featuring granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, a perfect blend of style and functionality. The attached 2-car garage ensures convenience, while the detached garage provides additional space for storage or a workshop area.  Step outside to your own oasis – a covered patio and fire pit invite you to relax and entertain in the backyard. With all these features and more, this home truly exemplifies modern living at its finest.  Don't miss the chance to make this stunning property yours!
